caption.text:
This Veterans Day, we at @projectrock are proud to support @ShepherdsMen and the SHARE Military Initiative at @ShepherdCenter with our 2024 #VetsDayCollection. üá∫üá∏
¬†
Through outreach, empowerment, and funding, Shepherd‚Äôs Men brings vital awareness and resources to the SHARE program‚Äîa lifeline for post-9/11 veterans and first responders impacted by traumatic brain injury and PTSD. This initiative provides life-changing, no-cost care, helping our heroes regain strength and renewed purpose.
¬†
Join us in supporting, link in bio. 

And THANK YOU to ALL our U.S. veterans for your service.

Ok this one got me - watch til the end ü•π‚ù§Ô∏è

This lovely girl was tearing up as we met, she said some beautiful things to me and asked if we could take a selfie - I said yes but first let‚Äôs take a few deep breaths together to compose ourselves a bit - we don‚Äôt want no crazy looking selfies ü§™ 

She was the absolute sweetest thing ü•∞

And to me, these kind of interactions with people will always always always be the best part of fame.

caption.text:
In all the chaos, emotions run high üò≠ 
I told this fan that I remembered exactly who he was, and where we first met 8 years ago - and even remembered. what we talked about. 
It clearly meant a lot to him as he got emotional. He said he had gone thru some rough times but now he‚Äôs stronger for it and thanked me. I was grateful to have this cool interaction with such an awesome fan. 

Also batshit strange how my crazy brain can remember exact and explicit things like this, but yet some days I can‚Äôt even remember if I put on deodorant üòÇüß† 

Love you back Germany üá©üá™‚ù§Ô∏è
#RedOneMovie #BerlinPremiere

caption.text:
This beautiful young lady in her wheelchair wrote me a letter ‚úçüèª and said I can read it later because this event was crazy with people everywhere, pulling at me. But I wanted to take some time and read it in front of her. Her loving words made me emo ü•π good thing I had my glasses on so no one could see my manly tears üòÖüí™üèæ

Thank you love for taking the time to write to me, and thank you for coming out ~ dj üñ§
